headline: Premier Medical Collaborates with Walgreens to Expand Access to Care Across Central Florida
summary: ORLANDO, Fla., July 16, 2025--Premier Medical, a leading primary and multispecialty care provider in Central Florida, today announces a new collaboration with Walgreens to increase access to high-quality healthcare in local communities.
